4. The HTML element .bg is given. Change the background color of this element to 'blue'.
* Code -> <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Change Background Color</title>
    <style>
        .bg {
            background-color: blue;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg">
        <!-- Content here -->
    </div>
</body>
</html>

//This CSS code changes the background color of elements with the class .bg to blue.